parameters.name: かわいいおもちゃ工場のテーマ

parameters:
\C[2]In the empty night station\C[0], a girl
stands alone. Her atmosphere gives off a
mysterious vibe.

\n<Detective>...! No one is here...!? And... when did it become
night...?
\n<Detective>...Do you know something? What exactly happened...
\n<???>I know, uncle ♥ I even know why you came here ♥

\n<Detective>...What on earth are you talking about? Stop
fooling around...

\n<???>But, I don't know uncle's name... I'm Luna, what
about you, uncle?

\n<Detective>...I am Detective. I am a detective dispatched
from the Police Agency.

\n<???>So, how is it going? Is the investigation
progressing smoothly? ♥

\n<Detective>...I'm sorry, but I can't disclose that kind of
information to civilians.

\n<???>You really have no idea about the cause, huh? The
\C[18]phenomenon of madness\C[0] ♥ Even though so
many of them are happening, you have no clue at
all. They'll call you incompetent ♥

\n<???>The phenomenon of madness ♥ There are so many
scary people overflowing ♥

\n<Detective>(Idiot... The phenomenon of madness is the code
name currently used within the investigative
agency...)

\n<Detective>(Why is a child like this... No, wait, if I show
any signs of agitation here, it will confirm...)

\n<???>Hehe ♥ It's fine if you deny it, but there's no
point in hiding it from Luna ♥

\n<Detective>(!?...No way... Can she read minds...? No, that's
ridiculous...)

\n<???>But what's happening right in front of your eyes
is reality, and everything that will happen from
now on is also reality ♥

\n<???>Luna, you know, I've started to desire you, Uncle
♥ Because Uncle seems to have a lot of things that
Luna wants ♥
\n<???>Hey, when was the last time you felt alive...?
\n<???>Living is an exciting thing, and it is enjoyable.
\n<???>Then, what makes you enjoy living, Uncle?

\n<???>Why don't you realize that the desire to eliminate
desire is the greatest desire of all?

\n<???>...Whose words were these again? Well, it's a
perfect quote for an uncle like me ♥

\n<???>Let me teach you ♥ The fate of desires, the joy of
life ♡
